236
00:19:43,773 --> 00:19:45,729
..posthypnotic suggestion.

237
00:19:45,813 --> 00:19:49,647
Did you leave anything else behind
when you were inside my brain?

238
00:19:49,733 --> 00:19:52,008
- Nothing!
- Tell the truth, Lisa.

239
00:19:52,093 --> 00:19:55,927
