You know, I have done this before.

240
00:19:56,893 --> 00:19:59,487
OK, good. I-l was... I was just making sure.

241
00:19:59,573 --> 00:20:01,643
It was just a harmless one anyway.

242
00:20:02,373 --> 00:20:04,728
- What?
- Did it actually work?

243
00:20:04,813 --> 00:20:07,691
- What did you say?
