you need to be a little more open-minded?

246
00:20:14,613 --> 00:20:17,286
- Yeah...
- So I just said that.

247
00:20:17,373 --> 00:20:21,286
''After you wake up, your mind will be
completely open, like an open door,...

248
00:20:21,373 --> 00:20:23,933
